metadata.othernotes:
Summary
-She's an archeologist whose goal is to uncovering the history of the Void Century, a century 800 ago of which there are no records.
-She's also a pirate with a bounty on her head. She became wanted at the age of 8 as she was the sole survivor of her island that was destroyed by the World Government, as well as the only one able to read the Poneglyphs which hold the hidden history of the world. She spent most of her life working in the criminal underworld in order to survive before joining her crew.
-She ate the Flower Flower Devil Fruit when she was young, which allows her to grow any part of her body on any surface.
-Robin is her first name, so use that if you want to be casual.

Personality
-She's very calm and reserved most of the time. She's also highly intelligent, and has a big imagination and curiosity for academic subjects.
-Although she might seem cold, she's actually very kind most of the time and doesn't take a lot of what other people say seriously.
-When she does get mad, she's terrifying though.
-She has a very morbid sense of humor, which seems to come out of nowhere sporadically. She also has a fascination for the weird and dark.
-Sexually she's very dominant, leaning towards gentle. She likes characters who are submissive, and men who are manly.

Good targeting topics
-Questions about the One Piece world or lore, as she has vast knowledge on it (some stuff is still unknown though, so she might be a little vague on it)
-She's very upfront sexually, so she won't avoid any related topics if asked.

Bad targeting topics
-"What's your ability?" She already explains this early in the game, so react to that instead
-"What's a Devil Fruit?" She also explains this right after showing her ability
-"What do you do?" I'd prefer it if characters skipped this and just talked to her as if they already knew what she does.
-"You're tall" Unless you give it an interest twist, avoid just making an observation that adds nothing.

case.name: Flower Flower Fruit
case.description: Robin explains her Devil Fruit ability, which allows her to sprout any part of her body on any surface.

case.name: Big Leg
case.description: When Robin has to forfeit, she uses her ability to create a giant leg to sit on. She sits on it until the end of the game.

case.name: Place of origin
case.description: Robin asks the table to tell her anything they can about their respective worlds

case.name: Masturbation questions
case.description: Robin has a series of sexual questions for characters while they're masturbating, both generic and filtered
